snippet.title: HIRAETH | Chapter 1 Game Trailer
snippet.description:
HIRAETH is an indie video game that features multiple mind-bending and complicated puzzles. Make your way through the test rooms and discover the secret behind the organization keeping you hostage.

Chapter 1 release date: 07.22.22
